metadata.name: Rejuvenation
metadata.description:
Upper Yosemite Falls rushes down the impressive granite cliffs as the early morning sun illuminates the spring meadow. The overflowing Merced River acts as a natural mirror providing the perfect reflection. A peaceful morning with just the sounds of the thunderous waterfall and chirping birds.
